00:12:57.333 --> 00:12:59.500
Communications and something else.

00:12:59.709 --> 00:13:01.041
REPORTER: So, I mean, I suppose in India,

00:13:01.250 --> 00:13:04.083
I mean, that it’s not as difficult to actually, um

00:13:04.291 --> 00:13:06.000
... to make people understand.

00:13:06.208 --> 00:13:09.333
It’s only when You start traveling abroad?

00:13:09.542 --> 00:13:11.542
SHRI MATAJI: Oh, Indians understand much better.

00:13:11.750 --> 00:13:12.750
REPORTER: That’s what I was saying.

00:13:12.959 --> 00:13:15.333
SHRI MATAJI: But abroad is the problem. Because, you see, they…

00:13:15.542 --> 00:13:17.500
they are naive, they don’t know.

00:13:17.709 --> 00:13:19.542
You see, Christ’s life was only for four years.

00:13:19.750 --> 00:13:22.333
He couldn’t tell them much about it; about the Holy Ghost.

00:13:22.542 --> 00:13:23.834
It’s all a mystery, you see.

00:13:24.000 --> 00:13:26.500
The Christianity could not give that, because they never went

00:13:26.709 --> 00:13:29.208
into the search of it, you see, the deeper of it.

00:13:29.458 --> 00:13:32.458
Just reading Bible, telling some sort of an interpretation

00:13:32.667 --> 00:13:33.834
doesn’t give you anything.

00:13:34.083 --> 00:13:36.959
So the second birth part of it they didn’t work out.

00:13:37.166 --> 00:13:39.959
And that’s why I find people got lost more,

00:13:40.125 --> 00:13:45.041
because of these gurus coming, giving them some ideas, this, that…

00:13:45.250 --> 00:13:48.125
And they sort of are hypnotized also to a great extent.

00:13:48.333 --> 00:13:50.166
All these people are hypnotized, brainwashed,

00:13:50.375 --> 00:13:52.709
then they, some of them went into drugs.

00:13:52.917 --> 00:13:56.625
You see, so many things, they are all self-destroying.

00:13:56.875 --> 00:14:00.375
That’s how I found people very much confused, very much confused.

00:14:00.625 --> 00:14:02.500
Of course, the people in India

00:14:02.709 --> 00:14:04.875
say, for example, of this entrepreneur,

00:14:05.041 --> 00:14:07.208
He knows I am a saint.

00:14:07.417 --> 00:14:09.458
