00:14:09.667 --> 00:14:11.333
and then he'll come to receive Me and…

00:14:11.542 --> 00:14:13.250
that even the Prime Minister of India,

00:14:13.458 --> 00:14:15.792
Mr. Lal Bahadur Shastri,  My husband was his secretary,

00:14:15.999 --> 00:14:19.375
but he used to come and see Me often, in the car, you see.

00:14:19.625 --> 00:14:22.458
