00:16:27.750 --> 00:16:30.291
who have no idea of a spiritual life, you see,

00:16:30.500 --> 00:16:32.291
if they try tricks, you see,

00:16:32.500 --> 00:16:35.583
like sex, you see, through sex and all that nonsense,

00:16:35.792 --> 00:16:39.667
then it feels insulted, and then there are problems.

