REPORTER: How can it be dangerous then?

00:16:41.875 --> 00:16:43.709
SHRI MATAJI: Beg your pardon? REPORTER: How, You said, it can be dangerous

00:16:43.917 --> 00:16:45.250
if it's not used properly?

00:16:45.458 --> 00:16:46.875
SHRI MATAJI: You see, like we could say that

00:16:47.041 --> 00:16:50.250
if I don’t know this instrument and I put My hand into something,

00:16:50.458 --> 00:16:52.917
