00:17:14.291 --> 00:17:16.542
sort of the thing you've got to try and make clear to people.

00:17:16.750 --> 00:17:18.709
SHRI MATAJI: Yes, you have to. And then, you see,

00:17:18.917 --> 00:17:21.834
when you get realization, you automatically become righteous,

00:17:22.000 --> 00:17:23.417
I don’t have to tell you “Become righteous.”

00:17:23.625 --> 00:17:25.709
Because the religion is enlightened within you.

00:17:25.917 --> 00:17:28.166
You automatically become. I don’t tell you that “You don’t drink,”

00:17:28.375 --> 00:17:30.417
you just don’t drink, because you don’t enjoy it any more.

00:17:30.625 --> 00:17:33.417
You don’t smoke, because you just don’t enjoy it; don’t take drugs.

00:17:33.625 --> 00:17:35.500
Just you just don’t do it because it’s all enlightened,

00:17:35.709 --> 00:17:37.625
because a new priority has come.

00:17:37.834 --> 00:17:40.583
Like if there’s light in this room, suddenly you start seeing

00:17:40.792 --> 00:17:42.166
where’s the position of everything,

00:17:42.375 --> 00:17:44.125
and you know, if you walk this way, you’ll be hit.

00:17:44.333 --> 00:17:46.500
In the same way, enlightenment means that

00:17:46.709 --> 00:17:48.333
automatically you become righteous.

00:17:48.583 --> 00:17:51.041
REPORTER: What is Your success rate in full for healing people?

00:17:51.250 --> 00:17:52.875
SHRI MATAJI: What is?… REPORTER: What is Your success rate

00:17:53.041 --> 00:17:54.583
for healing people who come to see You?

00:17:54.792 --> 00:17:56.291
SHRI MATAJI: Success? REPORTER: Successful or have helped them.

00:17:56.500 --> 00:17:58.500
REPORTER: How many times do You actually heal people

00:17:58.709 --> 00:17:59.667
compared to the number of people who come to see You?

00:17:59.875 --> 00:18:02.792
SHRI MATAJI: Oh, some people just come, for ten minutes is sufficient.

00:18:02.999 --> 00:18:06.417
Our president Sanjiva Reddy, the first president,

00:18:06.625 --> 00:18:09.083
he was coming from England… America.

00:18:09.291 --> 00:18:12.750
His operation had failed, he was just in a very bad shape.

00:18:12.959 --> 00:18:14.166
I just went to see him

00:18:14.417 --> 00:18:19.000
and he didn’t know I was Mataji, but he knew Me as Mrs. Shrivastav.

00:18:19.250 --> 00:18:21.542
And suddenly our High Commissioner told him,

00:18:21.750 --> 00:18:23.417
“This is Mataji Nirmala Devi.”

00:18:23.625 --> 00:18:26.583
So his wife said, “I’ve heard You have cured so many people,

00:18:26.792 --> 00:18:28.041
so just cure my husband.”

00:18:28.250 --> 00:18:30.583
I put My hand only for ten minutes, you’ll be surprised.

00:18:30.792 --> 00:18:32.041
He was just, then — he got it.

