00:18:38.667 --> 00:18:39.959
some people take less time.

00:18:40.125 --> 00:18:42.709
It depends on if they are complicated,

00:18:42.917 --> 00:18:46.750
you see, they take more time, some of them do.

00:18:46.959 --> 00:18:49.583
You see, for example, supposing I have to break through, now.

00:18:49.792 --> 00:18:52.333
And if you are just there, you will out.

00:18:52.542 --> 00:18:55.041
