00:19:12.083 --> 00:19:15.667
I don’t think, isn’t it?

00:19:16.250 --> 00:19:17.917
As far as I remember, I should say.

00:19:18.083 --> 00:19:20.166
REPORTER: Yeah, You've done quite a lot.

00:19:20.375 --> 00:19:22.000
SHRI MATAJI: You see, there are so many I have, it has happened,

00:19:22.208 --> 00:19:23.792
