00:19:23.999 --> 00:19:25.875
So there’s no end to it. Imagine,

00:19:26.041 --> 00:19:28.667
one person is Me, I can remember for Myself,

00:19:28.875 --> 00:19:30.458
but there are so many they are healing, and

00:19:30.667 --> 00:19:32.959
I just forget about it, I just don’t remember.

